basic.Peptide Name: Sparanegtin (natural AMPs; Crustaceans, arthropods, invertebrates, animals, BBS; UCLL1a)
basic.Target Organism: Active against Gram-positive B. subtilis, S. epidermidis, S. aureus and Gram-negative E. coli (MIC 25-48 uM), P. aeruginosa, P. fluorescens, S. flexneri, A. hydrophila (MICs 12-24 uM), and yeast C. neoformans and P. pastoris GS115 (MICs 24-48 uM).
